author: Reuters
title: European Factors to Watch on August 5
text: LONDON, Aug 5 Financial spreadbetters expected Britain's FTSE 100 to open 6-8 points or 0.1 percent higher, Germany's DAX to open 13-14 points or 0.1 percent higher, and France's CAC 40 to open 2-3 points or as much as 0.1 percent up.
